Christopher Connelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Connelly 0 Christopher Connelly (September 8, 1941 – December 7, 1988) was an American actor best known for his role as Norman Harrington in the successful prime time ABC soap opera Peyton Place. He stayed with the series during its entire five-year run (1964–1969).
